scopecontent.p:
The CIP records are arranged in the following series: Development Files
          Series; Printed Materials Series; Oversize Materials Series; Robert White Papers Series;
          Adam Isacson Papers Series; Selig Harrison Papers Series; Wayne S. Smith Papers Series;
          Geographic, Subject, and Program Files Series; and Audiovisual Materials
        Series.

Contains speeches in English and Spanish given by Isacson relating to Colombia;
              includes transparencies used by Isacson for his speeches. They are arranged
              alphabetically by subject name.
